<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/estilo.css">
    <script src="../js/slider.js"></script>
    <script src="../js/ham.js"></script>
    <title>Locean.</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <button class="header__button" id="btnNav" type="button">
            <i class="material-icons">menu</i>
        </button>

        <div id="logo_loceantext">
            <a href="/">
            <img id="logo__locean--text" src="../Imagens/Teste123.jpg" alt="locean-logo">
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <nav class="nav">
        <div class="nav__links">            
            <a href="/" class="nav__link nav__link--active">
                <i class="material-icons">home</i>
                Home
            </a>
            <a class="nav__link" href="/cursos">
                <i class="material-icons">article</i>
                Cursos
            </a>
            <a class="nav__link" href="/perfil">
                <i class="material-icons">person</i>
                Perfil
            </a>
            <a class="nav__link" href="/login">
                <i class="material-icons">login</i>
                Login
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="nav__overlay"></div>
    </nav>

    <section class="sec__carousel">
        <div class="carousel">
        <button class="carousel__button carousel__button--left is-hidden">
            <i class="material-icons">arrow_back_ios</i>
        </button>

        <div class="carousel__track-container">
            <ul class="carousel__track">
                <li class="carousel__slide current-slide">
                    <img class="carousel__image" src="../Imagens/Teste.jpg" alt="slide-1-carrousel">
                 </li>
                <li class="carousel__slide">
                   <img class="carousel__image" src="../Imagens/Slide-1.jpg" alt="slide-2-carrousel">
                </li>
                <li class="carousel__slide">
                   <img class="carousel__image" src="../Imagens/Slide-2.jpg" alt="slide-3-carrousel">
                </li>
                <li class="carousel__slide">
                   <img class="carousel__image" src="../Imagens/Slide-3.jpg" alt="slide-4-carrousel">
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div> 

        <button class="carousel__button carousel__button--right">
            <i class="material-icons">arrow_forward_ios</i>
        </button>

        <div class="carousel__nav">
            <button class="carousel__indicator current-slide"></button>
            <button class="carousel__indicator"></button>
            <button class="carousel__indicator"></button>
            <button class="carousel__indicator"></button>
        </div>
    </div>
    </section>

    <section class="sec__prop">
        <h1><strong>Conquiste</strong> seus objetivos com um único clique!</h1>
        <a href="/signin">
        <button class="button__prop">Vamos!</button>
    </a>
    </section>

    <section class="sec__prop1">
        <div class="sec__propbac">
            <h1><strong>O poder</strong> que o conhecimento nos dá, é o <strong>de alcançar</strong> locais que jamais imaginaríamos estar.<br>
                <br>
                Aprenda quando, onde e como quiser! <strong>Embarque</strong> nessa jornada e explore seus talentos nesse mar de conhecimentos.
            </h1>
        </div>
    </section>


    <div class="footer-container">
        <div class="footer">
            <a href="/contato"><i class="material-icons">email</i>
            Contato</a>
            <a href="/termos"><i class="material-icons">description</i>
            Termos de Serviço</a>
            <a href="/segurança"><i class="material-icons">shield</i>
            Segurança</a>
            <a href="/privacidade"><i class="material-icons">lock</i>
            Privacidade </a>
            <a href="/Aboutus"><i class="material-icons">text_snippet</i>
            Sobre Nós</a>
            <a href="/perguntas"><i class="material-icons">textsms</i>
            Perguntas Frequentes</a>
        </div>
    </div>

